text: Jubzhang Jubzhang is a archer from Bhutan. Jubzhang competed at the 1992, 1996 and 2000 Summer Olympics.Jubzang JUBZANG He was born on 7 May 1971.Jubzang Jubzang == References == Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Bhutanese archers Category:Olympians for Bhutan
